body: I can't belive that the comments are back, such a time we are in, a pandemic time nonetheless

A solid 7.5/10. Fantastic art, some of the best Elise art I've ever seen. Only I'm not sure she'd be okay with this but then again she might not know but then again she did seduce Kamui so... But my biggest complaint is "big brother" and "big sister" not exactly how Nohrians would address each other (even though in the game both kingdoms speak Japanese so that being said maybe) but it still is awkward in English (at least to me) oh well these are all minor complaints
